Basic knowledge of the technique of different athletics events and the skills to perform different athletics events at the elementary level. Various contemporary exercises will be introduced and basic practical knowledge will be provided to perform these exercises. General knowledge of competition regulations, which allow participation in athletics competitions.Objectives/eesmärkid:  Provide basic theoretical and practical knowledge about track and field and acquire the basics of different athletics techniques at the elementary level.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  After course student: has acquired basic knowledge on the history of athletics has acquired the technique of various athletics events at the elementary level knows and can purposefully use the training exercises of athletics based on the basic principles of sports training has acquired knowledge on the competition rules of athletics that enable him/her to take part in athletics competitions.
